    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >整栋大楼被封锁。居民们孤立无援。未能妥善藏身的人们步履蹒跚地穿过走廊，已然被感染。但危险不仅来自于感染者，黑暗中还隐藏着更多异象。整栋大楼仿佛活了过来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你会试图逃离，还是去寻找那些被遗忘的人们？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197890/extras/3bee79d21663651340aa0143b5e35118.poster.avif?t=1763061863\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197890/extras/3bee79d21663651340aa0143b5e35118.webm?t=1763061863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197890/extras/3bee79d21663651340aa0143b5e35118.mp4?t=1763061863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>生存恐怖与现代迷宫探索的融合</strong>：体验融合了生存恐怖与迷宫探索 RPG 元素的独特玩法，每一个决定都可能决定你的生死。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>快节奏的回合制战斗</strong>：运用策略，与各种噩梦般的生物展开激烈战斗。收集武器和物品，用策略和资源管理应对各种威胁。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>特雷弗·亨德森笔下的怪异生物</strong>：探索被诅咒的建筑和闹鬼场景，遭遇特雷弗·亨德森笔下的恐怖生物，直面与大名鼎鼎的“警笛头”、“长马”、“桥梁蠕虫”等众多作品一脉相承的标志性恐怖艺术风格。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多重路径：</strong>扮演幸存居民，用钢管和自制武器杀出重围；或是操控前来调查的警官，努力消除威胁并拯救其余幸存者。选择武器，掌握特殊技能，直面前方的危险。挣扎求生。随机应变。并以全新的方式回归。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>经典恐怖作品的启发</strong>：重现传奇作品的氛围，将探索、策略战斗和故事叙述融为一体。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197890/extras/94d91c79be72680fba689447f1b4aa84.poster.avif?t=1763061863\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197890/extras/94d91c79be72680fba689447f1b4aa84.webm?t=1763061863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197890/extras/94d91c79be72680fba689447f1b4aa84.mp4?t=1763061863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
